Problem Statement : 
	Write a java program to take the user input as a sentence from the user and count the total
	Number of words present in the sentence. And display the output as shown below.
	
		sentence--->  I am Learning Java.
		Output :	Total No.of words are : 4
					word 1 : I
					word 2 : am
					word 3 : Learning
					word 4 : Java 
					
Explanation :
	The program should accepts a sentence as a string from the user. Then convert the string into 
	String type of array by using the split() method. Now the no.of Words present is equals to the length
	of the array. Displaying the total no.of words as the length of the array. By using the for Loop
	the words were displayed according to their indexes. 